				Internal<span style="letter-spacing:1pt"> </span>CSS<span style="letter-spacing:1pt"> </span>is<span style="letter-spacing:0.9pt"> </span>used<span style="letter-spacing:1pt"> </span>to<span style="letter-spacing:1.05pt"> </span>apply<span style="letter-spacing:0.95pt"> </span>CSS<span style="letter-spacing:1pt"> </span>on<span style="letter-spacing:1.05pt"> </span>a<span style="letter-spacing:1.1pt"> </span>single<span style="letter-spacing:0.95pt"> </span>document<span style="letter-spacing:1.05pt"> </span>or<span style="letter-spacing:1.05pt"> </span>page.<span style="letter-spacing:1pt"> </span>It<span style="letter-spacing:1pt"> </span>can<span style="letter-spacing:1pt"> </span>affect<span style="letter-spacing:1.05pt"> </span>all<span style="letter-spacing:1.05pt"> </span>the elements of the page. It is written inside the style tag within head section of html.
