				background-color:<span style="letter-spacing:1.05pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">linen;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:4.9pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt">}</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:6.2pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt">
				h1<span style="letter-spacing:-0.25pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt">{</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:4.9pt; margin-left:72.1pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				color:<span style="letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> red;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:6.1pt; margin-left:71pt; margin-bottom:0pt">
				margin-left:<span style="letter-spacing:1.15pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.2pt">80px;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:4.9pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt">}</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:4.45pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">&lt;/style&gt;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:1.85pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">&lt;/head&gt;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:3.15pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">&lt;body&gt;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:1.9pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'">&lt;h1&gt;</span>The<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>internal<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>style<span style="letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span>sheet<span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt"> </span>is<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>applied<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>on<span style="letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span>this<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>heading.<span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">&lt;/h1&gt;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:3.25pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'">&lt;p&gt;</span>This<span style="letter-spacing:-0.25pt"> </span>paragraph<span style="letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span>will<span style="letter-spacing:-0.25pt"> </span>not<span style="letter-spacing:-0.25pt"> </span>be<span style="letter-spacing:-0.25pt"> </span>affected.<span style="letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:1.85pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">&lt;/body&gt;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:3.15pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">&lt;/html&gt;</span>
			</p>
			<h1 style="margin-top:3.05pt; margin-left:23pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-align:justify; font-size:22pt">
				External<span style="letter-spacing:-0.9pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.25pt">CSS</span>
			</h1>
			<p style="margin:15.8pt 5.9pt 0pt 23pt; text-align:justify; line-height:116%; font-size:12pt">
				The external style sheet is generally used when you want to make changes on multiple pages. It is ideal for this condition because it facilitates you to change the look of the entire web site by changing just one file.
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0.1pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				&#xa0;
			</p>
			<p style="margin:0pt 6.15pt 0pt 23pt; text-align:justify; line-height:116%; font-size:12pt">
				It uses the &lt;link&gt; tag on every page and the &lt;link&gt; tag should be put inside the head <span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">section.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0.05pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				&#xa0;
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:23pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">Example:</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:3.2pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				&#xa0;
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">&lt;head&gt;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:3.15pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'">&lt;link</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.95pt"> </span>rel="stylesheet"<span style="letter-spacing:-0.75pt"> </span>type="text/css"<span style="letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">href="mystyle.css"</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">&gt;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:2pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">&lt;/head&gt;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin:14.9pt 6.2pt 0pt 23pt; text-align:justify; line-height:116%; font-size:12pt">
				The external style sheet may be written in any text editor but must be saved with a .css extension. This file should not contain HTML elements.
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0.15pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				&#xa0;
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:23pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				Let's<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>take<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>an<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>example<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>of<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>style<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>sheet<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>file<span style="letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span>named<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">"mystyle.css".</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:2.15pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				&#xa0;
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:23pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10.5pt">
				<em>File:</em><em><span style="letter-spacing:-0.05pt"> </span></em><em><span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">mystyle.css</span></em>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:6.8pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10.5pt">
				<em>&#xa0;</em>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0.05pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				body<span style="letter-spacing:0.65pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt">{</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:4.9pt; margin-left:72.1pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				background-color:<span style="letter-spacing:1.15pt"> </span>light<span style="letter-spacing:1.15pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">blue;</span>
			</p>
		</div>
		<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both; mso-break-type:section-break" >
		<div>
			<p style="margin-top:5.45pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt">}</span>
