				&#xa0;
			</p>
			<p style="margin:0pt 6pt 0pt 23pt; line-height:116%; font-size:12pt">
				Note:<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt"> </span>You<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt"> </span>should<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt"> </span>not<span style="letter-spacing:-0.4pt"> </span>use<span style="letter-spacing:-0.45pt"> </span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt"> </span>space<span style="letter-spacing:-0.4pt"> </span>between<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt"> </span>the<span style="letter-spacing:-0.4pt"> </span>property<span style="letter-spacing:-0.4pt"> </span>value<span style="letter-spacing:-0.4pt"> </span>and<span style="letter-spacing:-0.4pt"> </span>the<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt"> </span>unit.<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt"> </span>For<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt"> </span>example: It should be margin-left:20px not margin-left:20 px.
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0.15pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				&#xa0;
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:23pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				Let's<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>take<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>an<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>example<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>of<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>style<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>sheet<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>file<span style="letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span>named<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">"mystyle.css".</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:2pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				&#xa0;
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0.05pt; margin-left:23pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10.5pt">
				<em>File:</em><em><span style="letter-spacing:-0.05pt"> </span></em><em><span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">mystyle.css</span></em>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:6.8pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10.5pt">
				<em>&#xa0;</em>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				body<span style="letter-spacing:0.65pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt">{</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:5.05pt; margin-left:72.1pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				background-color:<span style="letter-spacing:1.15pt"> </span>light<span style="letter-spacing:1.15pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">blue;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:4.95pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt">}</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:4.9pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				h1<span style="letter-spacing:-0.25pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt">{</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin:3pt 331.55pt 0pt 72.1pt; line-height:137%; font-size:12pt">
				color: navy; margin-left:<span style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt"> </span>20px;
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:1.7pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt">}</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:2.4pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				&#xa0;
