			<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:23pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				The<span style="letter-spacing:-0.05pt"> </span>background<span style="letter-spacing:0.1pt"> </span>looks better<span style="letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span>if<span style="letter-spacing:-0.05pt"> </span>the<span style="letter-spacing:0.1pt"> </span>image repeated<span style="letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span>horizontally<span style="letter-spacing:-0.05pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">only.</span>
			</p>
