				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'">background-repeat:</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:2.8pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'">repeat-</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.25pt">y;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:15.85pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				&lt;!DOCTYPE<span style="letter-spacing:0.1pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.2pt">html</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">&gt;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:1.85pt; margin-left:59pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">&lt;html&gt;</span>
