				The<span style="letter-spacing:-0.75pt"> </span>border-width<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>property<span style="letter-spacing:-0.75pt"> </span>is<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>used<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>to<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>set<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>the<span style="letter-spacing:-0.75pt"> </span>border's<span style="letter-spacing:-0.75pt"> </span>width.<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>It<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>is<span style="letter-spacing:-0.75pt"> </span>set<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>in<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt"> </span>pixels.<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>You<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>can<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>also use the one of the three pre-defined values, thin, medium or thick to set the width of the <span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt">border.</span>
