				<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">It is shorthand for </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'">border top-left-radius, border-top-right-radius, border-bottom- </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">right-radius</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">and</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">border-bottom-left-radius</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">It</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">gives</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">the</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">rounded</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">shape</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">to</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">the</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">corners</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">of </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">the border of an element. We can specify the border for all four corners of the box in a single declaration</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">using</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.3pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">the</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">border-radius.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">The</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.25pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">values</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">of</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">this</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">property</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.3pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">can</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">be</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">defined</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">in</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">percentage</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><s