				<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">If the bottom-left value is omitted, then it will be same as the top-right. If the value of bottom- right</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">is</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">eliminated,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">then</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">it</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">will</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">be</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">same</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">as</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">the</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">top-left.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">Similarly,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">if</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">top-right</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">is</s