				<span style="font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:10pt">o</span><span style="width:12pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt">Similarly,</span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.5pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt">when this</span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.05pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt">property</span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.05pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt">has four</span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt">values</span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.45pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.3pt">(border-radius:</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.3pt">10%</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.3pt">30%</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.3pt">20%</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.3pt">40%;)</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt">then </span>the first value will be the radius of top-left, the second value will be used for the top-right,
