			<p style="margin:13.85pt 6pt 0pt 23pt; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">In HTML,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">we</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">use</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">the</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">button</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">tag</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.25pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">to</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">create</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">a</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">button,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">but</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">by</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.35pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">using</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.25pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">CSS</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">properties,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">we</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">can</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">style</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'">the buttons. Buttons help us to create user interaction and event processing. They are one of the widely used elements of web pages.</span>
