			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:13.05pt; margin-left:23pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-align:justify; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'">normal:</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-1pt"> </span>It<span style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt"> </span>is<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>the<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>default<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>font-weight<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>whose<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>numeric<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>value<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>is<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.2pt">400.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="margin:12.95pt 5.7pt 0pt 23pt; text-align:justify; line-height:106%; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'">lighter:</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> </span>It<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>considers<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>the<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>existing<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>font-weight<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span>of<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>the<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>font-family<span style="letter-spacing:-0.75pt"> </span>and<span style="letter-spacing:-0.8pt"> </span>makes<span style="letter-spacing:-0.75pt"> </span>the<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>font-weight lighter compare to the parent element.
