				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'">bolder:</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> </span>It considers the existing font-weight of the <a href="https://www.javatpoint.com/css-font-family" style="text-decoration:none"><u><span style="color:#000000">font-family</span></u></a><span style="letter-spacing:-0.05pt"> </span>and makes the font- weight heavier compare to the parent element.
