			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:13.25pt; margin-left:23pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:107%; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'">number:</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-1pt"> </span>It is used to set the font-weight based on the specified number. Its range can be between 1 to 1000.
			</p>
