			<p style="margin:15.8pt 6.2pt 0pt 23pt; text-align:justify; line-height:116%; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="color:#333333">CSS outline is just like CSS border property. It facilitates you to draw an extra border around an element to get visual attention.</span>
