				&#xa0;
			</p>
			<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:23pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-align:justify; font-size:12pt">
				<span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; color:#333333">See</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.5pt; color:#333333"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; color:#333333">this</span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.5pt; color:#333333"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial Black'; letter-spacing:-0.1pt; color:#333333">example:</span>
